{"tid":272495,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"«蝻»港足前隊長李偉文遇劫失820萬 警拘3南亞漢","createTime":"2017-06-06T01:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T03:00:29.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fd1f02abe5c3f128cae2c5ff2f00ea49ce9906b","tid":272495,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:09:29.000Z","msg":"上月底香港足球代表隊前隊長李偉文在紅磡遇劫，近日有突破性發展，警方拘捕4名涉案男子，正追緝在逃同黨及約820萬元贓物下落。<br />\n其他報道：【六四28年】香港眾志街站籌得17.8萬 不及去年一半<br />\n被捕4名男子，分別3名南亞漢及1名本地男子，26歲至42歲，涉嫌行劫罪名。消息稱，案發後西九龍總區重案組探員經調查，本月3日至4日根據資料突擊搜查深水埗、尖沙嘴及九龍城多個目標地點，拘捕4人；案件仍在調查中，不排除再有人被捕。<br />\n上月24日晚近9時，43歲香港足球代表隊前隊長李偉文，拖着一個行李篋準備離開紅磡都會道6號置富都會商場之際，突遭4至5名南亞漢持刀撲出指嚇及襲擊，混亂間，南亞漢搶去李內藏24條金條（約750萬元）及1000萬日圓（約69.3萬元）的行李篋，乘接應客貨車逃去。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170606/s00001/1496681760214?google_editors_picks=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170606%2Fs00001%2F1496681760214%3Fgoogle_editors_picks%3Dtrue&d=Rq9gFWrYpwVjoItm5vmgSb5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=eedf346e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170606%2Fs00001%2F1496681760214%3Fgoogle_editors_picks%3Dtrue&h=f657e937\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170606/s00001/1496681760214?google_editors_picks=true</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170606/s00001/bc2a61a9af536df8f304383e7de024ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170606%2Fs00001%2Fbc2a61a9af536df8f304383e7de024ad.jpg&h=4d2f85d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港越來越多打劫強姦案同南亞有關了"},{"pid":"ea6fb71fa4fabf78a277cfb3e799e42a9f169c53","tid":272495,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:11:51.000Z","msg":"點解咁多金屌"},{"pid":"fad9117c9a36173f354007652124f506bbb5de11","tid":272495,"uid":389,"like":